50|$|The Silent Glider M was {{designed}} {{to comply with the}} Fédération Aéronautique Internationale microlight category and the US FAR 103 Ultralight Vehicles rules. It features a cable-braced rigid hang glider-style high-wing, weight-shift pitch <b>controls</b> and aerodynamic <b>roll</b> <b>controls,</b> a single-seat enclosed cockpit with a bubble canopy, retractable tricycle landing gear and a single engine in pusher configuration.|$|R
